name: Every Good Boy Does Fine... Right?
description:
3D Printed Companion :)

A sketch of a treble clef made into a 3D Object for my 'Choir Club' collection. Tap on the object in AR to hear an unreleased single from the album 'Cowboy Carta'- A Cat Album exclusively produced by KilljoyInk. 

Follow my twitter @killjoyartclub for all updates on 3D printed companions + links to purchase.

Choir Club.
